items.title: Trump tariffs live updates: Trump addresses stock market losses, China trade deficit
items.description: Trump's universal 10% levy against all countries went into effect early Saturday.

items.title: Democrats hammer Trump for his weekend of golf as stocks tumble
items.description: Dow futures opened Sunday evening down 1,500 points, or 4% percent., while the S&P 500 and NASDAQ 100 futures were also down 4%.

items.title: Speaker Johnson cuts deal with Rep. Luna over parental proxy voting
items.description: Speaker Mike Johnson and Florida GOP Rep. Anna Paulina Luna say they have cut a deal to end the fight over proxy voting for new parents.

items.title: Trump admin live updates: Bondi says Trump will 'probably' leave after second term
items.description: The administration's FEMA funding freeze violated a court order, a judge ruled.

items.title: Booker: Biggest mistake Democratic Party has made is ‘not centering people enough’
items.description: The biggest mistake Democrats have made is “not centering people enough” Sen. Cory Booker, D-N.J., said Sunday on ABC News' "This Week."
